      "instruction": "<p><strong>Return</strong> the dry, non-stick pan to a high heat, and once very hot, add the halloumi steaks</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cook</strong> on each side for 1-2 min, or until golden</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tip:</strong> If you don't have a non-stick pan, use a little oil</p>",
